summary: A Mod that includes 7 new races with their own Lore.
descriptionHtml:
[color=Red][b][size=4][b][size=4]Dear Nexus Moderators, if i am somehow breaking a rule, please give me a warning or send me a PM instead of just instant ban, i am always willing to correct humbly any wrong doing.[/size][/b][/size][/b][/color]



[color=yellow][b][size=5]Many thanks to everyone who has Endorsed or otherwise expressed their appreciation for this mod, thanks to all of you!![/size][/b][/color]



[b][color=#ff7700][size=4]ABOUT[/size][/color][/b]


SkyTest - MysticLands adds new races with their own Lore.



[b][color=#ff7700][size=4]INSTALL[/size][/color][/b]


Unrar SkyTEST.esp & textures folder and place them inside Data Folder which is located inside Main SKyrim folder.



[b][color=#ff7700][size=4]UNINSTALL[/size][/color][/b]



Create a new game without the mod, due the current state of the mod uninstall is not recommended...



[b][color=#ff7700][size=3]Version History
[/size][/color][/b]

Click the Changes Tab to see a list of Changes.



[color=#ff7700][size=4][b]FUTURE PLANS[/b][/size][/color]


I plan to add random encounters of GroobaOrks, more mercenaries for hire and follower, i am also working on the lore of the new Elven Races included in version 1.1 as a .txt file, i will include this file into the compressed rar.



[b][color=#ff7700][size=4]CREDITS[/size][/color][/b]

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_25
files.changelogHtml:
* Removed many aspects of the mod and left only the New Races
* Optimized file structure for smoother gameplay
* Tweak my races for balanced gameplay.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_27
files.changelogHtml: * Fixed minor issue with face tint

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_30
files.changelogHtml:
* Tweaked Elven Male Preset Faces for a slightly better look.
* Racial Powers can now be cast any time.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_31
files.changelogHtml: * Elven Males has been given new textures.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_33
files.changelogHtml:
* Removed few hairstyles for male elves that did not fit.
* Rebuild the mod with v1.6.89.0 of the CreationKit

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_34
files.changelogHtml:
* Added more Lesser Racial Powers to each of the Elven races
* Fixed few issues with the hair color
* Modified few Male Elven Presets
* Added couple more Hairstyles for Female Elves

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_35
files.changelogHtml:
* Further balance to Silimaurë Skills and Racial Powers.
* All Silimaurë now have a Penalty of 50% more damage from Poison.
* Massively improved the Preset Appearance of Silimaurë Races.
* Silimaure Female Races now uses new Mesh Body (CBBE).
* Silimaure Male Races now use new Hairless Texture.
* Gave unique Bodies and Textures to Silimaurë races.
* Male Ork Gröba uses new bulky Mesh Body and Textures.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_36
files.changelogHtml: * Rebuild the mod with 1.8.151.0 of the CreationKit.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_40
files.changelogHtml:
* Corrected neck/hand/feet texture issues in the bodies of all races.
* Further increased the Ork Appearance.
* Corrected minor issues with racial spells.
* Removed couple Hairstyles and added new and better ones for female Silimaurë

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races 1_45
files.changelogHtml:
* Added Diamond Silimaure Teen Race
* Added Diamond Silimaure Teen Innocent Voice Type
* Added new Unique Texture Clothes to Anarade & Drona

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands Races v1_50
files.changelogHtml:
* Improved all Silimaure Appearance.
* Revised Lore.
* Ehlanna can now be a follower.
* Drona has unique voice Set.
* Anarade has unique voice Set.

files.name: SkyTEST - MysticLands - Anarade Texture Fix
files.changelogHtml:
* Improved all Silimaure Appearance.

* Drona has unique voice Set.

files.changelogHtml:
